---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import { ArrowRight, CheckCircle2, Phone } from '@lucide/astro';
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
import ajCallegan from '../assets/images/aj-callegan.jpg';
import contactImage from '../assets/images/imgi_226_premium_photo-1677782977189-d2ba571a679c.jpeg';
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Contact ACC Building Performance | Book Your Assessment"
  description="Contact ACC Building Performance, local to the Gulf South and serving the entire United States, to book a building science assessment, compliance test, HVAC design, or healthy home consultation."
>
  <section class="hero-airflow hero-noise relative isolate overflow-hidden bg-[#0b4850] px-5 pb-24 pt-36 text-white sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-32">
    <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto grid max-w-6xl items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_0.78fr]">
      <div class="text-center lg:text-left">
        <p class="text-[0.62rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#86c8dc] sm:text-[0.72rem] sm:tracking-[0.34em]">Contact</p>
        <h1 class="mt-4 max-w-4xl text-5xl font-black leading-[0.98] tracking-tight sm:mt-8 sm:text-7xl">Let's Find Your Home's Answer.</h1>
        <p class="reveal-body mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg font-semibold leading-8 text-white/63 sm:mt-8">Fill out the form below and AJ will follow up with you personally. No automated systems. No call centers. A real conversation with the person who will actually do the work.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal-body overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-[#0f545e] shadow-2xl shadow-black/20">
        <Image src={contactImage} alt="New home framing during construction" width={760} class="aspect-[1.02] w-full object-cover" loading="eager" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-acc-mist px-5 py-24 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
      <section class="reveal-body mb-12 overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-[#eaf6f9] shadow-2xl shadow-[#06333a]/12 ring-1 ring-[#cfe3e7] lg:grid lg:grid-cols-[0.44fr_1fr]">
        <div class="min-h-[22rem] bg-[#cfe3e7]">
          <Image src={ajCallegan} alt="AJ Callegan, founder of ACC Building Performance" width={720} class="h-full w-full object-cover object-bottom" />
        </div>
        <div class="relative px-7 py-9 text-[#063f46] sm:px-10 lg:px-14 lg:py-12">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_85%_10%,rgba(127,194,208,0.2),transparent_18rem)]"></div>
          <div class="relative">
            <h2 class="max-w-xl text-4xl font-black leading-[1.04] tracking-tight text-[#063f46] sm:text-5xl">A Note From AJ</h2>
            <div class="mt-6 grid max-w-2xl gap-4 text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-[#164f59]/86">
              <p>When you reach out to ACC Building Performance, you're not entering a sales funnel. You're starting a conversation with me directly.</p>
              <p>I know you've probably tried other things. I know you may have spent money that didn't produce results. I know you might be skeptical about whether this is going to be any different.</p>
              <p>What I can tell you is this: if something is wrong with your home, I will find it. I will document it clearly. And I will tell you exactly what it means and what needs to happen about it, honestly, directly, and without any agenda other than getting you the right answer.</p>
              <p class="pt-2 text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#063f46]">AJ, ACC Building Performance</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="grid items-start gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_0.55fr]">
      <form name="contact" method="POST" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="company" class="rounded-2xl border border-[#d5ded9] bg-white p-7 shadow-2xl shadow-[#06333a]/10 sm:p-9">
        <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="contact" />
        <p class="hidden"><label>Company <input name="company" /></label></p>
        <div class="grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858] sm:col-span-2">Full name *<input name="full_name" required class="form-field" /></label>
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858]">Phone number *<input type="tel" name="phone" required class="form-field" /></label>
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858]">Email address *<input type="email" name="email" required class="form-field" /></label>
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858] sm:col-span-2">Home address *<input name="home_address" required class="form-field" /></label>
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858]">Square footage of the home *<input type="number" name="home_square_footage" min="0" required class="form-field" /></label>
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858]">Number of bedrooms in home *<input type="number" name="bedrooms" min="0" required class="form-field" /></label>
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858]">Number of bathrooms in home *<input type="number" name="bathrooms" min="0" step="0.5" required class="form-field" /></label>
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858]">How many levels does the home have? *<input type="number" name="home_levels" min="1" required class="form-field" /></label>
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858]">What year was the home built? *<input type="number" name="year_built" min="1600" max="2100" required class="form-field" /></label>
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858]">Builder's name<input name="builder_name" class="form-field" /></label>
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858]">What year did you move into the home? *<input type="number" name="move_in_year" min="1600" max="2100" required class="form-field" /></label>
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858]">Number of heating and cooling systems<input type="number" name="heating_cooling_systems" min="0" class="form-field" /></label>
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858] sm:col-span-2">Heating and cooling contractor's name<input name="heating_cooling_contractor" class="form-field" /></label>

          <fieldset class="grid gap-3 text-sm font-black text-[#254858]">
            <legend>Is the attic vented/unconditioned? *</legend>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm font-bold text-[#365563]">
              <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-2"><input type="radio" name="attic_vented_unconditioned" value="Yes" required class="h-4 w-4 accent-[#0b6b78]" /> Yes</label>
              <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-2"><input type="radio" name="attic_vented_unconditioned" value="No" required class="h-4 w-4 accent-[#0b6b78]" /> No</label>
            </div>
          </fieldset>

          <fieldset class="grid gap-3 text-sm font-black text-[#254858]">
            <legend>If the home has a crawlspace, is it vented?</legend>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm font-bold text-[#365563]">
              <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-2"><input type="radio" name="crawlspace_vented" value="Yes" class="h-4 w-4 accent-[#0b6b78]" /> Yes</label>
              <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-2"><input type="radio" name="crawlspace_vented" value="No" class="h-4 w-4 accent-[#0b6b78]" /> No</label>
            </div>
          </fieldset>

          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858]">Number of adults living in the home *<input type="number" name="adults_in_home" min="0" required class="form-field" /></label>
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858]">Number of children living in the home *<input type="number" name="children_in_home" min="0" required class="form-field" /></label>
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858] sm:col-span-2">Number and type of pets living in the home *<input name="indoor_pets" required class="form-field" /></label>
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858] sm:col-span-2">Number and type of pets outside the home *<input name="outdoor_pets" required class="form-field" /></label>
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858] sm:col-span-2">
            Any specific health concerns believed to be associated with the indoor built environment *
            <textarea name="health_concerns" rows="5" required class="form-field resize-y"></textarea>
          </label>
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858] sm:col-span-2">
            When did you first notice any health symptoms after moving into your current home? *
            <textarea name="symptom_timing" rows="4" required class="form-field resize-y"></textarea>
          </label>
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858] sm:col-span-2">
            Is there anything in particular you're worried about or would like me to focus on? *
            <textarea name="assessment_focus" rows="4" required class="form-field resize-y"></textarea>
          </label>
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858] sm:col-span-2">
            What are you hoping to achieve through this assessment? *
            <textarea name="assessment_goals" rows="4" required class="form-field resize-y"></textarea>
          </label>
          <label class="grid gap-2 text-sm font-black text-[#254858] sm:col-span-2">How did you hear about ACC Building Performance? *<input name="referral_source" required class="form-field" /></label>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn-primary mt-7">
          Send My Message
          <ArrowRight class="h-5 w-5" />
        </button>
      </form>

      <aside class="grid gap-6">
        <section class="rounded-2xl border border-[#d5ded9] bg-white p-7 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#063f46]">What Happens Next</h2>
          <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4">
            {[
              'AJ reviews your information and reaches out personally, typically within one business day.',
              'You have a real conversation about your home, your situation, and whether an assessment is the right next step.',
              'If you move forward, we send you an intake form and get your assessment scheduled.',
            ].map((step) => (
              <p class="flex gap-3 text-sm font-bold leading-6 text-[#365563]">
                <CheckCircle2 class="mt-0.5 h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-[#0b6b78]" />
                <span>{step}</span>
              </p>
            ))}
          </div>
          <p class="mt-6 text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-[#5c7178]">There's no pressure. Just a conversation with someone who genuinely wants to help you figure out what's going on.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="rounded-2xl border border-[#d5ded9] bg-white p-7 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#063f46]">Local to the Gulf South. Serving Nationwide.</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base font-bold leading-7 text-[#365563]">ACC Building Performance is based in the Gulf South and serves families, contractors, and project teams across the entire United States.</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-[#5c7178]">After you submit, AJ will follow up by phone or email within one business day. If your situation is urgent, you are also welcome to call or text directly.</p>
          <a href="tel:+15042480186" class="mt-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-base font-black text-[#0b6b78]">
            <Phone class="h-5 w-5" />
            504-248-0186
          </a>
        </section>
      </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
